<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٤٨-<span class="c5"> أَخْبَرَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ عَلِيٍّ حَدَّثَنَا الْأَثْرَمُ أَنَّ أَبَا عَبْدِ اللَّهِ قَالَ لَهُ رَجُلٌ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">أَوْصَانِي أَخِي بِكَفَّارَاتٍ قَالَ:</span> أَعْطِ مُدَّ مُدَّ فَإِنْ تَطَوَّعْتَ عَنْهُ بِأَكْثَرَ جَازَ؟<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[قَالَ: نَعَمْ]</span> .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> فَيَلْحَقُ ذَلِكَ الْمَيِّتَ؟<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> نَعَمْ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>